AI Mechanic Advisor

A professional AI-powered advisor for bikes, cars, engines, and general maintenance.
Built with Flask, OpenAI GPT, and a modern Bootstrap frontend. Stores conversation history locally and can show similar past cases.

Features

rofessional mechanic advice for bikes, cars, engines, and electrical systems

 Shows similar past cases (optional RAG integration)

 Local conversation history (last 10 messages)

Loading spinner & responsive UI

Easy to extend for Supabase integration or private mode

Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS (Bootstrap), Vanilla JS

Backend: Python, Flask

AI: OpenAI GPT-3.5 / GPT-4 (optional upgrade)

Optional: Supabase for semantic search / RAG

Installation

Clone the repo

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ai-mechanic-advisor.git
cd ai-mechanic-advisor


Install dependencies

pip install flask openai python-dotenv


Create a .env file

OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxx-your-openai-key
FLASK_SECRET_KEY=super_secret_key
SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url       
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_key   


Run the app

python app.py


Open in browser: http://127.0.0.1:5000

Project Structure
├─ public/
│  ├─ index.html       
│  ├─ app.js           
│  └─ styles.css      
├─ app.py             
└─ .env               

Usage

Select a category (bike, car, engine, maintenance, electrical)

Describe your problem in the text area

Click Get Advice

View AI response, similar cases, and conversation history

Optional Upgrades

 User login + private mode

 RAG with Supabase or other vector DB

 Mobile-first UI

 Supabase Edge / production deployment
 
 Rate-limiting & safety checks